title: Rainfall and Sunshine's Correlation with Car Crashes
description: This project explores the impact of weather conditions—specifically rainfall and sunshine—on car accident rates. By analyzing real-world data, it aims to uncover patterns and correlations that could help improve road safety measures and accident prevention strategies.

title: Harmony Messaging App
description: Harmony is a modern messaging application designed for seamless communication. Inspired by platforms like Discord, it offers real-time chat, voice communication, and community features, all wrapped in a user-friendly interface. The app focuses on reliability, performance, and user engagement.

title: Hidden Markov Movie Recommender
description: This project utilizes Hidden Markov Models (HMMs) to create an intelligent movie recommendation system. By analyzing user behavior and sequential patterns, it predicts and suggests movies that align with individual preferences, improving recommendation accuracy over time.
